item.title: Item.cfg
item.dc:creator: @spon80 spon80
item.description:
@spon80 wrote:

im pretty sure the first 3 are the shop prices and alchemy prices

EDITx3

(quote from Zachery?)
Now listen closely, you cannot edit these without know what zero is what bonus here is what each zero stands for!!!
FIRST FIVE 0’s = ALL ATTACK BONUSES
1st 0= stab att bonus
2nd 0 = slash att bonus
3rd 0 = crush att bonus
4th 0 = magic att bonus
5th 0 = range att bonus

NOW THEN THE NEXT FIVE o’s = ALL DEFENSE BONUSES
6th 0 = stab def bonus
7th 0 = slash def bonus
8th 0 = crush def bonus
9th 0 = magic def bonus
10th 0 = range def bonus

THE LAST TWO 0’s = STRENGTH AND PRAYER BONUSES
11th 0 = strength bonus
12th 0 = prayer bonus
(unquote from Zachery?)

Happy?
